CM_ BO_ 113 "MLX90640 front-right summary. Region meaning is fixed as R0=upper-left, R1=upper-right, R2=lower-left, R3=lower-right inside the sensor field of view. Each region is encoded as integer byte + fractional byte (0.01 degC).";
CM_ BO_ 114 "MLX90640 front-left summary. Region meaning is fixed as R0=upper-left, R1=upper-right, R2=lower-left, R3=lower-right inside the sensor field of view. Payload layout is identical to FR.";
CM_ BO_ 115 "MLX90640 rear-left summary. Region meaning is fixed as R0=upper-left, R1=upper-right, R2=lower-left, R3=lower-right inside the sensor field of view. Payload layout is identical to FL.";
CM_ BO_ 116 "MLX90640 rear-right summary. Region meaning is fixed as R0=upper-left, R1=upper-right, R2=lower-left, R3=lower-right inside the sensor field of view. Payload layout is identical to FL.";

CM_ SG_ 113 R0_Integer "Front-right sensor Region 0 integer part. Region 0 = upper-left quadrant of the sensor image. Final temperature = R0_Integer + R0_Fraction.";
CM_ SG_ 113 R0_Fraction "Front-right sensor Region 0 fractional part, unit 0.01 degC. Region 0 = upper-left quadrant. Example: Integer=23, Fraction=45 means 23.45 degC.";
CM_ SG_ 113 R1_Integer "Front-right sensor Region 1 integer part. Region 1 = upper-right quadrant of the sensor image. Final temperature = R1_Integer + R1_Fraction.";
CM_ SG_ 113 R1_Fraction "Front-right sensor Region 1 fractional part, unit 0.01 degC. Region 1 = upper-right quadrant.";
CM_ SG_ 113 R2_Integer "Front-right sensor Region 2 integer part. Region 2 = lower-left quadrant of the sensor image. Final temperature = R2_Integer + R2_Fraction.";
CM_ SG_ 113 R2_Fraction "Front-right sensor Region 2 fractional part, unit 0.01 degC. Region 2 = lower-left quadrant.";
CM_ SG_ 113 R3_Integer "Front-right sensor Region 3 integer part. Region 3 = lower-right quadrant of the sensor image. Final temperature = R3_Integer + R3_Fraction.";
CM_ SG_ 113 R3_Fraction "Front-right sensor Region 3 fractional part, unit 0.01 degC. Region 3 = lower-right quadrant.";

